  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nIn the most recent version of Chrome, it's not possible to download files from a sandboxed frame, unless the allow-downloads flag is set. However, if a sandboxed frame calls window.open with the noopener option and a download URL, the download will proceed. This is true"
